Description: Android Dropbox Account Info contains Dropbox account information recovered from a Kindle device.
Android Dropbox contains Dropbox file information recovered from a Kindle device.

Android Call Logs (UFED Agent) contains calling logs from the Phone application on Android. These logs are recovered from <incoming_calls>, <outgoing_calls>, <missed_calls>, <unknown_calls> tags found in a UFED Report.xml.

Android Contacts (UFED Agent) contains information recovered from the Contacts application on Android. These contacts are recovered from <contacts> tag found in a UFED Report.xml.
Android Contacts contains contact information from a recovered Android device.

Android Facebook Messenger Attachments contains information about files shared within Facebook Messenger. Picture and video files are valuable when investigating a suspect's computer for illicit content. Media content can help an examiner identify victims in cases of child abuse material and exploitation. In a corporate environment, pictures can contain scans of confidential documents, easily shared through file sharing.
Android Google Hangouts Messages contains the messages from Google Hangouts from an Android device.
Android Kik Messenger Attachments contains the attachments of messages from Kik Messenger from an Android device.
Android Kik Messenger Contacts contains information about a user's Kik Messenger contacts.
Android Kik Messenger Messages contains Kik Messenger messages that were sent or received by the local user.
SMS/MMS messages sent and received using Android Messages.
Android MMS (UFED Agent) contains MMS messages sent or received using the Messages app on Android. These messages are recovered from <mms_messages> tags found in a UFED Report.xml
MMS messages sent or received using an Android device. These messages are recovered from mmssms.db.
Android SIM Card Information is information about the device's SIM card that is recoverable if the user has the Android Messages application installed on the device.
Android SMS (UFED Agent) contains SMS messages sent or received using the Messages app on Android. These messages are recovered from <sms_messages> tags found in a UFED Report.xml.
SMS/MMS messages sent or received using an Android device. Data for this artifact is recovered during the acquisition process using an Android Content Provider.
SMS and MMS messages sent or received using an Android device. These messages are recovered from icing_mmssms.db.
SMS and MMS messages sent or received using an Android device. These messages are recovered from mmssms.db.
SMS messages sent using the Messages app on Android.
Android TextNow Calls contains information about calls and voicemails that are sent and received through the TextNow application.
Android TextNow Chat contains chat messages that are sent and received through the TextNow application.
Android TextNow Contacts contains the application, phone, email and group contacts that a user has in the TextNow application.
Android TextNow Groups contains membership information for TextNow group chats.
Android TextNow Profile contains TextNow user profiles and application preference settings.
Android TigerText Messages contains messages from the TigerText Android application.
WhatsApp Accounts Information Contains the login information for the user's account, including the private key used for authentication.

WhatsApp Chats contains information about chat sessions that occur between the local user and another user or group. This artifact indicates the IDs of each participant as well as information about unread messages and the time when the last message was sent.
Android WhatsApp Contacts contains contacts that were added to WhatsApp by the local user.
Android WhatsApp Groups contains information about the WhatsApp Group chats that the user participates in.

Android WhatsApp Live Locations captures Live Locations that are shared with the local device user. The coordinates in each result represent the sender's last shared location. Once a Live Location expires, it is no longer recoverable.
Android WhatsApp Messages contains messages that were sent and received using WhatsApp.
Android WhatsApp Profile contains profile pictures that WhatsApp uses that are stored locally.
WhatsApp User Profiles contains profile information about the local WhatsApp user.
Contains the BBM Contacts recovered from an Android device.

Burner Contacts contains information about a subject's Burner Contacts, as recovered from their Android device.

Cake Local User Account contains information about the logged in local user.
Cake Messages contains messages sent and received by the local user.
Chatous Chat Messages contains messages that were sent and received using the Chatous application.
Chatous Chat Partners contains information about the users that the local user has communicated with.

Discord Logged-in Account contains information about the user that is currently logged into Discord on the device. Information about other accounts that were previously logged into are not recoverable.

Discord Messages contains information about messages and calls that are sent and received using Discord. Messages from some channels might be missing if they haven't been cached by the application. This artifact uses both parsing and carving techniques to recover messages.

Facebook Messenger Calls contains call data recovered from Facebook Messenger. Provides useful background information on a suspect, including who he or she is communicating or associated with. Status and location updates in social media can also provide location information about the suspect.

Facebook Messenger Groups contains data about group chats on Facebook Messenger. Provides useful background information on a suspect, including who he or she is communicating or associated with. Status and location updates in social media can also provide location information about the suspect.

Facebook Messenger Messages contains messages recovered from Facebook Messenger. Provides useful background information on a suspect, including who he or she is communicating or associated with. Status and location updates in social media can also provide location information about the suspect.

Facebook Messenger Users Contacted contains information about users contacted from the device using Facebook Messenger. Status and location updates in social media can provide detail on where the suspect has been. In addition, this artifact provides background information on a suspect,including who he or she is communicating or associated with.
Glide Messages contains messages sent and received by the local user.
Glide Users contains information about the contacts that the local user has added using Glide. The local user's contact information is also recovered by this artifact.
Google Duo Activity contains details about audio calls, video calls, and messages sent and received by the user.
Google Duo Group Calls contains details about the video calls made and received by the user.
Google Duo Groups contains membership information of Google Duo Groups.
Google Hangouts Cached Images contains the cached images from Google Hangouts from an Android device.
Google Hangouts Voice Calls contains a history of voice calls between the local user and other users.
Google Meet Meeting History contains the meetings that any local user on the device has joined.
GroupMe Accounts contains information about the accounts that the local user has logged in with on the device.
GroupMe Contacts contains information about a user's contacts.

Gtalk Contacts contains contact information that was recovered from Gtalk.
Gtalk Message contains the details of messages that were recovered from Gtalk.
Houseparty Messages contains messages recovered from Houseparty.
Houseparty Users contains information about the users that were contacted from the device using Houseparty.
imo Contacts contains information about a user's contacts.
imo Messages contains information about sent and received messages and calls made using the imo application.

ooVoo Chat History contains the chat history between the data owner and their contacts.

QQ File Transfers contains file transfers recovered from the QQ application.
QQ Local Users contains local users recovered from the QQ application.

SIM Card ICCID contains the ICCID number that identifies the device's SIM card.

Your Phone Companion Info contains information about the computers that are synced to the local device using Your Phone, and information about the types of data are synced from device to computer.

Evernote Work Chat contains messages sent and received by the local user.
Google Keep Notes contains information about the notes that have been accessed using Google Keep on the device.
Hangul Word Processor specifies information about files that were created using Hangul Word Processor.
Samsung Notes contains information about the notes that a user has created on their Samsung device.

Thinkfree Office Viewer Files contains information about the files that the user has opened using Thinkfree Office Viewer. Even if the user has deleted the file from the device, this artifact can still recover information about the file if they opened it in the viewer.
Android Emails contains the email fragments that were recovered from an Android device.
Android Gmail Conversations contains information about email conversations between the local user and others, as recovered from an Android device.

Google Calendar Calendars contains a list of all the calendars the user has synced to their Google account.

ProtonMail is a free end-to-end encrypted email service. ProtonMail Contacts contains information about contacts messaged through the email application ProtonMail.
ProtonMail is a free end-to-end encrypted email service. ProtonMail Emails contains information about emails sent and received with ProtonMail.

Android KeyStore - GrayKey contains passwords and tokens from the Android GrayKey image, reading the 'android_keystore' file generated by the GrayKey tool.

Android Google Maps contains information about the locations that a user searches for using Google Maps.
Wi-Fi Profiles contains a list of the saved Wi-Fi Profiles on a mobile device.
Google Maps Directions contains information about directions queries requested by the user using Google Maps.

Google Maps Saved Locations contains information about locations that the user may have saved as places of interests, such as their home and work locations, places they've starred, and places they want to go to. Users can also create their own custom location lists to add locations to. These locations will synchronize between different devices on Google Maps when signed into the same account.
Last Known Locations contains a list of the last known locations of the Android device, as tracked by the GPS receiver and recovered using dumpsys.
Contains information about all the OnStar RemoteLink accounts found on the device.

Waze Events can contain information about upcoming trips that a user has planned.

Calc Vault Browser Bookmarks contains the webpages a user has saved while using Calc Vault.
Calc Vault Browser History contains information about the webpages a user has visited using Calc Vault.

Camera History contains a list of the instances where applications have accessed the camera functionality on a device. This artifact can show when an application package accesses camera functionality, which can help the investigator determine when a suspect may have been using their device's camera.
Google Photos Albums contains information about the albums recovered from the device.
Google Photos Comments contains information about comments left on an album or individual media by users.
Google Photos Media contains information about media items added to Google Photos.

Private Photo Vault Albums contains information about the albums a user creates to organize their media in the Private Photo Vault application. The album information can be useful intelligence for how a user might have organized encrypted media.

Private Photo Vault Media contains information about encrypted media files that  the user stores in the Private Photo Vault application. If decryption is successful, the decrypted media content is made available in this artifact. Metadata about the encrypted media files, such as timestamps, are always available. Users will often resort to encrypted media applications for storing illicit material. Being able to decrypt this media can be crucial to a case.

On Android, Private Photo Vault does not explicitly reference thumbnails in the database. Further, multiple resolutions can exist. This artifact will decrypt all of the thumbnails found in the thumbnails directory.

Skype Calls contains information about Skype calls that occured between users.
Skype Chat messages contains Skype chat messages sent from one user to another.
Skype Chatsync Messages contains Skype messages sent from one user to another that are parsed from the chatsync directory.
Skype Contacts contains information about Skype contacts that are recovered, which may or may not be added contacts.
Skype Emotions contains reactions from users on Skype messages.
Skype File Transfers contains files that are transferred from one user to another using Skype.
Skype Group Chat contains information about the Skype group chats that a user is a part of.
Skype IP Addresses contains IP addresses that are associated with a Skype user account.
Skype Notifications contains notifications shown to users on Skype.
Skype SMS contains SMS messages that a user sends or recieves using Skype.
Skype Voicemails contains voicemails that a user sends or recieves using Skype.
Slack Accounts contains account information on accounts signed onto the local device.
Slack Channel Messages contains messages sent or received in channels in the user's Slack workspace.
Slack Channels contains information about each of the channels and conversations that exist in a user's Slack workspace.
Slack Direct Messages contains information about direct messages sent or received in 1:1 chats or group chats.
Slack Files contains information about any files that have been saved to the Slack workspace. Files may or may not have been shared with other users.
Slack Users contains information about each user in the Slack workspace.
Snapchat Cached Videos contains videos stored by the Snapchat application on iOS
Snapchat Chat Messages contains the chat messages sent between users.
Snapchat Contacts contains information about the user's Snapchat friends as well as contact information from the user's device that was requested by the Snapchat application.
Snapchat Conversations - iOS contain information about all the chats recovered from the local device.
Snapchat Group Members contains information about participants of the groups that the local user is a member of.
Snapchat Memories contains pictures and videos that the Snapchat user saves as a memory.
Snapchat My Story - iOS contains information about a collection of Snaps which can exist for a 24 hour period.
Snapchat Stories contains information about a collection of snaps, which can exist for a 24 hour period.
Snapchat Story Snaps contains information about snaps that have been posted to a story.
TamTam Messenger Channels contains messages that belong to channel conversations recovered from the local device. The user must be subscribed to the channel in order to receive the messages.
TamTam Messenger Contacts displays information about the TamTam contacts associated with the local user's account (including the local user).
TamTam Messenger Conversations contains information about all chats recovered from the local device, including individual, group, channel and draft messages.
TamTam Messenger Groups contains all messages that belong to group conversations recovered from the local device.
TamTam Messenger Messages contains all individual messages (one-to-one) recovered from the local device.
iOS Telegram Channel Chats contains information about the channel chats that the suspect participates in using the Telegram application.
iOS Telegram Chats contains information about the chats that the suspect participates in using the Telegram application.
iOS Telegram Messages contains individual chat messages that are sent and received using the Telegram application.
iOS Telegram Users contains information about the various users that the suspect has encountered using Telegram, either directly or as part of a channel chat.
Textfree Attachments contains attachments from the iOS Textfree application.
Textfree Contacts contains the contacts from the iOS Textfree application.
Textfree Groups contains information about group chats from the iOS Textfree applications.
Textfree Messages contains messages from the iOS Textfree application.
TextMe Calls contains information about the calls that the suspect participates in using the TextMe application.
TextMe Conversations contains details about all the conversations the local user is a part of.
TextMe Messages contains individual chat messages that are sent and received using the TextMe application.
TextNow Calls contains information about calls and voicemails that are sent and received through the TextNow applications.
TextNow Chat contains chat messages that are sent and received through the TextNow application.
TextNow Profile contains the TextNow user's profile and application preference settings.
TextPlus Calls contains call information from TextPlus data on an iOS device.
TextPlus Messages contains message information from TextPlus data on an iOS device.
Threema Messages contains messages sent and received by the local Threema user.
Threema Users contains information about the various users that the suspect has encountered using Threema.
Viber Messages contains details about sent or received Viber messages on an iOS device.
WeChat Friends contains stored contact information for the WeChat application on iOS.
WeChat Messages contains stored messages for the WeChat application on iOS.
Wickr Me Conversations contains details about all the Individual, Group, and Room conversations the local user is a part of.

Wickr Me Messages contains decrypted and decoded messages sent or received by a Wickr Me user on iOS. These messages can include text messages, call logs, transmitted locations, attachments such as pictures and videos, voice messages, and more.
Wickr Me Users contains details about the users the local user has interacted with in the app.
Zalo Contacts contains the user's Zalo contacts.
Zalo Groups contains Zalo groups that the user participates in.
Zalo Messages contains messages or calls sent or received using Zalo.
Zalo Profiles contains profile information for the local Zalo user.
Zello Messages provides information about the various messages the user has sent and received on the app.
Zello Profiles provides information about the various profiles and channels the user has interacted with on the app.
Zoom Channels contains information about the channels that the local user participates in.
Zoom Chat Messages contains details about Zoom chat messages sent outside of a meeting.
Zoom Contacts contains information about a user's Zoom contacts.
Zoom Meeting Messages contains details about Zoom chat messages sent during a meeting.
Zoom User Accounts contains details about the local user's zoom account.
Amazon Alexa Audio Activity contains details about audio activity detected by the Amazon Alexa application.
Amazon Alexa Device Information contains details about Alexa-enabled devices.
Amazon Alexa Tasks contains details about shopping lists or other tasks tracked by the Amazon Alexa application.
Amazon Alexa User contains details about user accounts recognized by the Amazon Alexa application.
Amazon Alexa Web Resource contains details about Amazon API resources contacted by the Amazon Alexa application.

Apple Health Distance specifies the distances traveled during activities that were tracked by the iOS device. This data could be synced from another device, such as an Apple Watch. Data about the distance, steps, floors, workout, and heart rate of a user can be particularly useful as it provides a look at a user's activity level at any given time.

Apple Health Floors specifies the number of floors climbed during activities that were tracked by the iOS device. This data could be synced from another device, such as an Apple Watch. Data about the distance, steps, floors, workout, and heart rate of a user can be particularly useful as it provides a look at a user's activity level at any given time.

Apple Health Heart Rate specifies the average heart rate during activities that were tracked by the iOS device, which will be synced from an Apple Watch. Data about the distance, steps, floors, workout, and heart rate of a user can be particularly useful as it provides a look at a user's activity level at any given time.

Apple Health Steps specifies the number of steps taken during activities that were tracked by the iOS device. This data could be synced from another device, such as an Apple Watch. Data about the distance, steps, floors, workout, and heart rate of a user can be particularly useful as it provides a look at a user's activity level at any given time.

Apple Health Workout specifies the duration of the activity that was tracked by the iOS device. This data could be synced from another device, such as an Apple Watch. Data about the distance, steps, floors, workout and heart rate of a user can be particularly useful as it provides a look at a user's activity level at any given time.
Bluetooth Devices contains the Bluetooth devices that the iOS device has paired with.
CarPlay Connected Cars provides information about the different cars that have been connected to the device through CarPlay.
CarPlay Recently Used Applications provides information about applications that have been recently used through CarPlay.
A list of the Apple user's device and device info registered within the Find My application.
A list of the Apple user's items registered within the Find My application.
A list of crowdsourced or safe locations for the Apple user's device/items registered within the Find My application.
Fitbit Activity Log specifies the activities that were tracked by the Fitbit.
Analyzing this data can help identify the number of floors a user has traveled within a day.
Fitbit Profiles specifies information from the Fitbit profiles that the user has set up on the device.
Fitbit Sleep contains information about the user's sleep patterns.
Fitbit Steps specifies information about the number of steps a person takes while wearing the Fitbit. Steps are aggregated for a 60 minute interval and then stored.

Latent Wireless Geolocated WiFi Hotspots contains information about WiFi hotspots that were discovered using a Latent Wireless device. Latent Wireless stores information about the hotspots in a database that Magnet AXIOM can parse for details about each hotspot.
Nest Location Configuration contains configuration and settings related to the structure housing the Nest system.
Nest Temperature Adjustment contains details about thermostat temperature adjustments made through the Nest application.
Nest User contains details about Nest user accounts.
Pebble Activity Information specifies the physical activities that were tracked by the Pebble watch.
Pebble Calendar Events contains calendar events that are displayed on the Pebble Watch Timeline.
Pebble Physical Characteristics specifies the user's activity profile information.
Pebble Steps specifies the steps information tracked by the Pebble smart watch.
Pebble Weather Locations contains location information that's tracked by the Pebble Watch.
Seen Bluetooth Devices keep track of Bluetooth devices that may have been seen by the host device.
SIM Card Activity contains information about the SIM cards that have been used in an iOS device.
SIM Card ICCID contains the ICCID number that identifies the device's SIM card.
SIM Card IMSI contains IMSI numbers used to identify the mobile subscriber, as recovered from the SIM card.
SIM Card Phone Numbers contains records of all the phone numbers saved to the device SIM card. The type of number is indicated by the record type.
SIM Card Service Providers contains the names of mobile service providers that the device has connected with, and which are recovered from the SIM card.
SIM Card SMS Messages contains messages sent or received by the local user which were saved to the SIM card.

Your Phone Contacts contains information about contacts synced from a mobile device to a computer using Your Phone. The Your Phone application can sync data from Android and iOS devices to computers running Windows 10.
Your Phone Devices contains information about the devices that are synced to the user's computer by using the Your Phone application.

Your Phone Pictures contains information about pictures synced from a mobile device to a computer using Your Phone. The Your Phone application syncs the 25 most recently taken photos from Android and iOS devices to computers running Windows 10.

Your Phone SMS/MMS contains information about messages synced from a mobile device to a computer using Your Phone. The Your Phone application can sync data from Android and iOS devices to computers running Windows 10.
Apple Notes Voice contains the recovered voice notes from an iOS device.
Apple Notes contains information about the notes that a user has created on their iOS device.
Evernote Accounts contains information about the user accounts that have been used to log in on the device.
Evernote Contacts contains information about users that have communicated with the local user account.
Evernote Notes contains any notes associated with the local user, including notes shared from other users to the local user.
Evernote Work Chat contains messages sent and received by the local user.
Google Docs Items contains information about the documents and folders that have been accessed using Google Docs on the device.
Google Docs Thumbnails contains information about thumbnail pictures of the Google Docs documents found on the device.
Google Sheets Items contains information about the spreadsheets and folders that have been accessed using Google Sheets on the device.
Google Sheets Thumbnails contains information about the thumbnail pictures of Google Sheets spreadsheets found on the device.
Google Slides Items contains information about the presentations and folders that have been accessed using Google Slides on the device.
Google Slides Thumbnails contains information about thumbnail pictures of the Google Slides presentations found on the device.
iOS Reminders contains information about the reminders, such as due dates and to do lists, that a user has created and accessed in the Reminders app on their device.
Apple Mail contains the emails and the fragments of emails that have been extracted from an iOS device.
The iOS calendar application is a default application on iOS.
Gmail Emails contains the Gmail email fragments that were recovered from an Android device.
Google Calendar Calendars contains a list of all the calendars the user has synced to their Google account.
Google Calendar Events contains information about a user's calendar events on the Google Calendar application.
Google Calendar Reminders contains information about the reminders that a user has set in their calendars.
iOS Yahoo Mail Contacts contains contact details for local user accounts in iOS Yahoo Mail application.
iOS Yahoo Mail Messages contains emails stored by iOS Yahoo Mail application.
iOS Yahoo Mail User Accounts contains local user accounts for iOS Yahoo Mail application.
Microsoft Outlook is a personal information manager and email client. Outlook Appointments captures information related to appointments scheduled in Microsoft Outlook.
Microsoft Outlook is a personal information manager and email client. Outlook Contacts captures information related to contacts stored in Microsoft Outlook.
Microsoft Outlook is a personal information manager and email client. Outlook Messages captures information related to emails sent and received in Microsoft Outlook.

Apple Keychain Generic Passwords contains passwords for applications and services that are saved to the Keychain application. Analyzing results from this artifact can reveal valuable passwords and tokens that are associated with the user's accounts.

Apple Keychain Internet Passwords contains passwords for websites and internet services that are saved to the Keychain application. Analyzing results from this artifact can reveal valuable passwords and tokens that are associated with the user's accounts.
Apple Keychain Saved Credit Cards contain credit card entries saved to the Keychain application.
Apple Maps Favorites contains information about a user's favorited locations.
Apple Maps Searches contains searches generated by the user using Apple Maps.
Apple Maps Trips contains trips generated by Apple Maps. Instances of this artifact can be suggested routes as well as trips that the user actually takes.

Cached Locations stores a sample of locations that the iOS device has cached. Each instance contains the location, speed, and direction of travel at that particular point in time. The frequency that location samples are cached can vary depending on device usage, where some applications (such as Maps) can result in samples being cached very frequently.
iOS Google Map Coordinates contains Google map tile coordinates viewed on an iOS device.
iOS Maps contains images from iOS maps that were recovered from the device.
Wi-Fi Profiles contains a list of the saved Wi-Fi Profiles on a mobile device.
Lyft Account Information stores information associated with the user's account.
Lyft Last Known Location contains the application user's last known location as recorded by Lyft.
Lyft Location Shortcuts contains information about the locations for which the user has created shortcuts.
Lyft Rider Payment Details contains information about the user's payment profile.
OnStar RemoteLink Hotspot Info contains information about the vehicle WiFi hotspots associated with an OnStar account.
OnStar RemoteLink Remote Commands contains information about commands sent from the device.
OnStar RemoteLink Saved Wireless Carrier contains information about the wireless accounts associated with a vehicle.
OnStar RemoteLink Searches contains possible searched locations.
OnStar RemoteLink Vehicle Diagnostics contains information about the diagnostic values retrieved from the vehicle.
OnStar RemoteLink Vehicle Info contains information about the vehicle associated with the account.
Parked Car Locations contains the locations of a user's vehicle that they've saved and which are tracked by the iOS device.

Significant Locations Visits contains information about the saved significant locations that the user visits. These location visits are automatically tracked by the device when the user is in the vicinity.

Significant Locations contains information about places that are deemed to be significant in some way to the user. These locations can be manually added by the user (such as a home or work address) or are automatically added by Apple. This data is used to help make more personalized predictions.
Uber Accounts contains account information about riders, as recovered from the Uber application (passenger only).
Uber Cached Locations contains information about locations that Uber caches, such as the initial location at the time of application startup or locations from a trip (passenger only).
Uber Locations contains the latitude and longitude of various locations, as recovered from the Uber application (passenger only).
Uber Payments contains payment information associated with a user's Uber rides, as recovered from the Uber application (passenger only).
Uber Profiles contains information about a user's Uber profiles, as recovered from the Uber application (passenger only).
Uber Rider Payment Details contains information about the user's payment profile, such as their payment method and fare-splitting info (passenger only).
Uber Trips contains information about a user's Uber rides, as recovered from the Uber application (passenger only).
Waze Events can contain information about upcoming trips that a user has planned.
Waze Favorites contains information about the locations that a user has bookmarked as a favorite.
Waze Places contains all the places that the user has searched using Waze.
WiFi Locations contains records of WiFi Location detected by the mobile device at a given time.
Best Secret Folder Albums contains information on the albums that the user has created in the application.
Best Secret Folder Configuration Data contains information about the configuration of the application, including the locations where hidden media is stored.
Best Secret Folder Media contains information about the media files that the user has added in the application.
Google Photos Albums contain information about the albums recovered from the device.
Google Photos Comments contains information about comments left on an album or individual media by users.
Contains information about media items added to Google Photos.
iOS Device Wallpapers contains the home screen and lock screen pictures and information about wallpaper configurations used on a device.

iOS Snapshots contains stored snapshots of an application's state taken by iOS when the application is suspended. An application is suspended when it is sent to the background, either by minimizing the application or by switching to a different application.
Live Photos contains Live Photos that were retrieved using parsing. Support exists for all versions of iOS.
Photos Albums contains information about the albums that contain pictures and media in the Photos application on an iOS device.

Photos Media Information contains metadata about pictures and videos stored in the Photos application on an iOS device as well as any other accompanying media and modified media related to the original media file recovered.

Private Photo Vault Albums contains information about the albums a user creates to organize their media in the Private Photo Vault application. The album information can be useful intelligence for how a user might have organized encrypted media.

Private Photo Vault Media contains information about encrypted media files that the user stores in the Private Photo Vault application. If decryption is successful, the decrypted media content is made available in this artifact. Metadata about the encrypted media files, such as timestamps, are always available. Users will often resort to encrypted media applications for storing illicit material. Being able to decrypt this media can be crucial to a case.

Secret Photo Vault Albums contains information about the albums a user creates to organize their media in the Secret Photo Vault application. Users can create a fake account as a distraction from the content they want to hide in their main account.

Secret Photo Vault Application Passwords contains information about the passwords the user has set for the Secret Photo Vault Application. The fake password unlocks a sub-set of albums from the application, as determined by the user. The real password unlocks the entire application.
Secret Photo Vault Bookmarks contains information about the webpages that a user has bookmarked while using the browser of the Secret Photo Vault application.
Secret Photo Vault Break-In Alerts contains forward-facing pictures that are taken when the incorrect login passcode is provided.

Secret Photo Vault Contacts contains information about the contacts a user saved in the Secret Photo Vault application. Users can create a fake account as a distraction from the content they want to hide in their main account.

Secret Photo Vault Media contains information about the picture and video files that the user stores in the Secret Photo Vault application. Users can create a fake account as a distraction from the content they want to hide in their main account.

Secret Photo Vault Saved Passwords contains information about the passwords a user has saved while using the browser of the Secret Photo Vault application. Users can create a fake account as a distraction from the content they want to hide in their main account.
Secret Photo Vault Tabs provides information about the currently open browser tabs in the Secret Photo Vault's built in browser.

AirDrop Available Recipients lists all available recipients for an AirDrop transfer that was outgoing from the local device. The devices need to be in Bluetooth and WiFi range to connect to each other. You can recover up to one week of AirDrop activity history as it is stored in the Apple Unified Logs.
AirDrop Background Activity is a collection of logs that capture background events triggered by the AirDrop service.
AirDrop Discoverability lists changes to the discoverability status of device.

AirDrop Incoming Transfers lists information about AirDrop transfers incoming to the local device. The devices need to be in Bluetooth and WiFi range to connect to each other. You can recover up to one week of AirDrop activity history as it is stored in the Apple Unified Logs.

AirDrop Outgoing Transfers lists information about AirDrop transfers outgoing from the local device. The devices need to be in Bluetooth and WiFi range to connect to each other. You can recover up to one week of AirDrop activity history as it is stored in the Apple Unified Logs.

Apple Accounts contains information about the Apple ID accounts used on the macOS computer. The account details contained can help investigators recover and correlate account information across applications, and provide information on what accounts to review and get more information from.
Cell Tower Locations contains records of which cell towers a device connects to at a given time.
File System Events contains information about the changes to file system objects on an iOS device. This artifact contains all system event files recovered from the .fseventsd folder.
File System Information contains all of the relevant information about the hard drives in use by the operating system.
Google Accounts contains the Google accounts that are currently signed in on any Google application on the device.

iOS Home Screen Items contains information about the applications and folders on the Home screen, including their specific locations. This artifact shows how the user has organized applications on their Home screen and can help identify applications of interest.
Network Usage Application Data contains information about how an application sends or receives data over the network.
Network Usage Connections contains information about the networks that a device connects to.

Owner Information contains information about the iOS device and the device owner. Information includes the device name, the phone number associated with the phone, and other details associated with iOS.
PowerLog App Usage contains information about the applications that were running on the device during a specified interval.
PowerLog Application State contains information about application state transition.
PowerLog Battery Level contains information about the phone's battery.
PowerLog Battery Shutdown contains information about when the phone's battery completely runs out and shuts down.
PowerLog Camera State contains information about changes to the camera state which indicate when a device's camera is in use.
PowerLog Device Lock State contains information about when the phone was locked or unlocked.
PowerLog In Call Service contains information about when an application on the device was used to perform a call service.
PowerLog Lightning Cable Status contains information about when the phone had a lightning cable connected or disconnected.
PowerLog Process Data Usage contains information about the processes that were running on the device, and the amount of data that was sent and received during the specified interval.
PowerLog Screen Autolock contains information about when the phone autolocked.
PowerLog Timezone Information contains information about the timezones that were registered on the device.

Siri Message Search Suggestions contains the sent or received messages that Siri provides to the user as search results for a query. Queries can be typed in the search bar or spoken using Siri voice commands.
User Notification Events contains data of notifications that have occurred on an iOS device.
Beam Transactions provides information about any logged transactions that have been sent by the user on the app.
BRD Transactions provides information about any logged transactions that have been sent by the user on the app.
Coinbase Purchases provides information about any cached cryptocurrency purchases that have happened on the app. Cached purchase information may not exist in all cases.
Coinbase Transactions provides information about any cached cryptocurrency transactions that have been sent by the user on the app. Cached transaction information may not exist in all cases.
Coinbase Users provides information about the cached local user.

Coinomi Transactions provides information about any logged transactions that have been sent/received by the user of the application. These records are carved and should be verified as they may include compressed or truncated data.

Exodus Transactions provides information about any cached cryptocurrency transactions that have been sent or received by the user on the app. Cached transaction information may not exist in all cases.
Torrent Active Transfers contains information about the torrents that are active on the user's system.
Torrent Feeds contains information about RSS feeds that a user subscribes to that contains torrents available for download.
Torrent File Fragments contains data that is carved or parsed from .torrent files that are used to download torrents from various networks on the Internet.

Facebook Comments contains information about comments that have been cached on the device. A cached comment does not necessarily imply that the local account interacted with the comment, just that it was cached on the device. Further investigation should be performed to confirm the user's activity.

Facebook Posts contains information about posts that have been cached on the device. A cached post does not necessarily imply that the local account interacted with the post, just that it was cached on the device. Further investigation should be performed to confirm the user's activity.
Foursquare Check-ins contains check-ins made by the iOS Foursquare application.
Foursquare Locations contains locations cached by the iOS Foursquare application.
Grindr Buddies contains the buddies and their details within the current user's extracted iOS data.
Grindr Group Members contains the groups and their members within the current user's extracted iOS data.
Grindr Messages contains the messages and their details within the current user's extracted iOS data.
GROWLr Chat Messages contains messages stored by the iOS GROWLr application.
GROWLr Notes contains notes stored by the iOS GROWLr application.
Instagram Direct Messages contains Instagram direct messages that are sent or received by the local user.
Instagram Group Members contains information about the Instagram groups that the local user is a member of.
Instagram Media contains the media files that have been found inside the Instagram application.
Instagram Profiles contains all the profile information that the local user has had communications with, or have been referred to through direct messages communication.
iOS Facebook Friends contains the contact information of a user's friends stored by the Facebook application.
iOS Facebook Messages contains Facebook messages recovered from the device.
iOS Instagram Posts contains information about posts that a user has recently viewed on Instagram for iOS, as well as comments that are present on those posts.
iOS Tinder Accounts contains all of the recovered iOS Tinder accounts.
iOS Tinder Matches contains all of a user's recovered iOS Tinder matches.
iOS Tinder Messages contains all of a user's recovered iOS Tinder messages.
iOS Tinder Photos contains all of the recovered iOS Tinder photos.
iOS Whisper Posts contains the posts stored by the Whisper application.

Life30 Circle Members contains information about the members of a circle. A circle is comprised of a group of individuals, such as a family, that the local user has created or has been added to by another circle member.
Life360 Local User Account contains information about the local user account.
Life360 Messages contains messages sent and received by the local user within a circle that they're a member of.
Life360 Places indicates favorite locations that are saved by the user or the application.
Life360 Trip Locations indicates the locations that the user visits (or passes by on the way to a destination). During a trip, the application will log locations at regular intervals along the way.
LinkedIn Messages contains messages sent and received by the local user.
LinkedIn Profile contains information about the user accounts that the local user has used to log in on the device.
Musical.ly Local Users contains all of the users that have logged in to Musical.ly on the local device.
Musical.ly Messages contains the messages sent or received via the in-app message system of Musical.ly.
Musical.ly Posts contains posts that Musical.ly retrieved from the web.
Musical.ly Users contains all of the users that the local user has viewed in Musical.ly.
Parler Activity contains information about the posts and comments that the local user has accessed or made.
Parler Users contains information about the local user account and any other users they've interacted with.
Pinterest Accounts contains information about the Pinterest accounts that the local user has logged in with on the device.
Pinterest Boards contains information about the Pinterest boards created by local user.
Pinterest Messages contains messages or pins sent and received by the local user.
Pinterest Pins contains information about the items that the local user has pinned to their own board.
Reddit Accounts contains information about the user accounts that are used to log in to the Reddit application on the device.
Reddit Posts contains information about the posts recovered from the device. These posts might be ones that the user has read or created on their device.
Reddit Recently Visited Subreddits contains information about the subreddits that a user has recently visited while on their device.
Sina Weibo Posts contains user posts (similar to Twitter's tweets) on the Sina Weibo for iOS application.
Sina Weibo Private Messages contains stored data from private messages on the Sina Weibo for iOS application.
TikTok Contacts contains information about a user's contacts in TikTok.
TikTok Media contains media that were either viewed or created by the user.
TikTok Messages contains information about the messages a user sends or receives using TikTok.
Tumblr Activity provides information of how the Tumblr application accessed API URLs and any media that may accompany these requests.
Tumblr Blocked Blogs contains information about the blogs blocked by the local user.
Tumblr Chat Messages contains messages sent and received using Tumblr.
Tumblr Created Posts contains information about the blog posts created by the local user.
Tumblr Followed Blogs contains information about the blogs followed by the local user.
Tumblr Profiles contains information about the profiles encountered when using the Tumblr application.
Tumblr Tags contains information about the subject tags the local user has selected. Selecting a tags expresses the user's interest in a subject so they can see more content of that type.
Twitter Direct Messages contains carved and noncarved direct messages from the Twitter application. Note that carving may not retrieve the name and screen name of sender and receiver.
Twitter Tweets contains carved and noncarved tweets from the Twitter application. Note that carving older versions of the application will only recover the Tweet column.
Twitter Users contains information about users that were cached on the local user's device.
This artifact contains VK messages (either private or group messages) as well as the details about pictures, video, and audio that may have been sent.
This artifact contains the various VK users that the data owner has been in communication with, as well as the users own profile.
Whisper Messages contains the messages that were sent and received between the local user and others.
Yik Yak Notifications contains the notifications that have been generated for the user.
Yik Yak Yaks contains the Yaks the user has viewed on their homepage.
Aloha Bookmarks contains the webpages that a user has bookmarked.
Aloha Browser Downloads contains information about the files that a user downloads from the Internet.
Aloha Browser History contains information about the websites that the user visits.
Bolt Browser Bookmarks contains stored bookmark entries for the Bolt browser on iOS.
Bolt Browser History contains stored history entries for the Bolt browser on iOS.
Brave Bookmarks contain bookmarks that reference saved webpages.
Brave Favicons contains the favicons that Brave displays in the address bar when visiting a website. These icons are sometimes downloaded when you favorite/bookmark a website.
Brave Tab History contains the websites that the user visits in a particular tab, sorted by order in which they were visited.
Brave Web History contains a history of all the websites that the user visits (includes unique visits only).
Chrome Archived Keyword Search Terms contains keyword search terms that were archived by the browser.
Chrome Archived Web History contains an archived history of old webpage visits.
Chrome Autofill Profiles contains profiles that Chrome uses to fill in forms with saved values.
Chrome Autofill contains records of the autofill values that Chrome saves for different types of text fields.
Chrome Bookmarks contains browser bookmarks that reference saved webpages.
Chrome Cache Records contans content that Chrome downloads and caches to speed up rendering times. Cached content can include pictures, text, HTML, JavaScript, and more.
Chrome Cookies contains cookies that Chrome downloads from the Internet that contain information about the websites that a user visits.
Chrome Current Session contains information about the browser session that's currently underway.
Chrome Current Tabs contans information about the tabs that are open in the current browser session.
Chrome Downloads contains information about the files that a user downloads from the Internet.
Chrome FavIcons contains the favicons that Chrome displays in the address bar for the website that's currently displayed. These icons are sometimes downloaded when you favorite/bookmark a website.
Chrome History Index contains an index of the webpages that the user has visited in the past.
Chrome Keyword Search Terms contains information about the keyword search terms that a user enters.
Chrome Last Session contains information about the previous browser session.
Chrome Last Tabs contains information about the tabs that were open during the previous session.
Android Chrome Logins contains login information that a user provides in Chrome. Passwords are often encrypted, so you might not be able to recover them unless you're examining a live system.
Chrome Saved Credit Cards contains the credit card information saved by the user.
Chrome Shortcuts contains all of the shortcuts used by Google Chrome for user entered URLs.
Chrome Tab History contains a history of websites that the user has opened on each tab within the application. Each tab contains its own timeline of activity generated by the user.
